            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) In nomine domini Dei omnipotentis aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName> divina misericordia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Quia sacerdotibus et Deo famulantibus
                        temporale regiae dignitati conferre subsidium convenit, id circo noverit
                        omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac
                        futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Archchancellor #Bishops #fidelisOf"
                            ref="#people/216">Ardingum <rs
                                key="#Intercessory #Archchancellor #Bishops #fidelisOf"
                                >reverentissimum episcopum summumque cancellarium et dilectissimum
                                fidelem nostrum</rs></persName> suppliciter nostram exorasse
                        clementiam, quatenus quendam <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >massariolum iuris regni nostri</rs> situm <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/124"><rs key="#Comitatus">in comitatu
                            Veronensi</rs></geogName>
                        <geogName key="#Other_administrative_unit" ref="#estates/261"><placeName
                                key="#Other_administrative_unit" ref="#places/575"><rs
                                    key="#Other_administrative_unit">in valle Veriaco loco ubi
                                    dicitur <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/576"
                                        >Sortiago</placeName></rs></placeName></geogName>,
                        pertinentem <geogName key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            ref="#estates/135"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                                ref="#places/258"><rs
                                    key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention">de
                                    curte nostra quae Lazeses</rs></placeName>
                        </geogName>vocitatur, cum universis ad eundem massariolum pertinentibus ex
                        integro, nec non et <rs key="#Mills">quendam molendinum </rs>positum
                            <geogName key="#Other_administrative_unit" ref="#estates/261"><placeName
                                key="#Other_administrative_unit" ref="#places/575"><rs
                                    key="#Other_administrative_unit">in predicta valle loco qui
                                    dicitur <placeName key="#Mills" ref="#places/577">Pruno qui
                                        nominatur Spiculum</placeName></rs></placeName></geogName>,
                        pro Dei amore et remedio animae nostrae cuidam presbitero nomine <persName
                            key="#fidelisOf" ref="#people/334"><rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >Odelberto</rs></persName><rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"> iure
                            proprietario</rs> modis omnibus concedere dignaremur. Cuius precibus
                        acclinati predictum massariolum cum omnibus adiacentiis ac pertinentiis
                        suis, casis videlicet, terris, vineis, campis, pratis, vineis, silvis,
                        salectis, sacionibus, aquis aquarumque decursibus, seu cum omnibus que dici
                        vel nominari possunt ad se pertinentibus, seu et prenominatum molendinum
                        perpetuo iure eidem presbitero per hoc nostrae concessionis preceptum modis
                        omnibus concedimus atque donamus, et de nostro iure ac dominio in eius ius
                        atque dominium transfundimus et donamus, ut habeat, teneat, possideat
                        faciatque in omnibus quicquid eius decreverit animus vel voluntas,
                        potestatemque habeat donandi, vendendi, commutandi, alienandi, pro anima
                        iudicandi seu quicquid voluerit faciendi tam ipse quam sui heredes, absque
                        minoratione vel contradictione cuiusquam. Si quis igitur hoc nostrae
                        auctoritatis seu concessionis preceptum aliquando infringere aut violare
                        quesierit, sciat se procul dubio compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi
                            libras triginta</rs>, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camerae
                            pal[at]ii nostri</rs> et medietatem predic[to presbitero suisque
                        heredi]bus vel cui ipse aut ipsi habere conces[serint. Quod ut verius
                        credatur et diligentius ob]servetur, manu propria roboratum de anulo nostro
                        subter assignari prec[epimus.] Signum domni (MF) Berengarii serenissimi
                        regis. <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/619">Ambrosius <rs
                                key="#Chancellor">cancellarius </rs></persName>ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi <rs
                                key="#Archchancellor #Bishops">episcopi et archicancellarii
                                recognovi et subscripsi</rs></persName>. (SR) (SI n. 11) Data kal.
                        aug., anno dominice incamationis .DCCCCV., domni vero Berengarii serenissimi
                        regis .XVIII., indictione .VIII. Actum <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention" ref="#places/364"
                                ><rs key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            >Tulles</rs></placeName>. in Christi nomine feliciter, amen. </ab>
